WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.013 --> 00:00:06.089
Welcome to the 247HRM Helpdesk Agent Handbook.

2
00:00:06.343 --> 00:00:09.586
In ninety seconds, we'll log you in and tour the screen.

3
00:00:09.838 --> 00:00:13.249
Login is passwordless. Just your work email and a one-time code.

4
00:00:16.327 --> 00:00:18.773
Click Send OTP.

5
00:00:20.098 --> 00:00:23.351
Check your email — a six-digit code arrives in seconds.

6
00:00:25.557 --> 00:00:28.223
Click Validate to sign in.

7
00:00:29.838 --> 00:00:32.064
You land on the dashboard.

8
00:00:32.327 --> 00:00:35.068
Three regions repeat across every screen.

9
00:00:35.329 --> 00:00:38.922
Top — the global bar. Timezone, notifications, your role.

10
00:00:39.178 --> 00:00:42.946
Left — the sidenav. Each link is a module you have access to.

11
00:00:43.198 --> 00:00:46.188
And the main area, which changes as you navigate.

12
00:00:46.439 --> 00:00:49.229
Most days you'll spend in Tickets.

13
00:00:49.835 --> 00:00:51.290
Let's open it.

14
00:00:52.371 --> 00:00:54.009
Your inbox.

15
00:00:54.281 --> 00:00:57.869
Six counters at the top show today's pulse.
